                        <interp inst="t18400914-name-590" type="given" value="HORATIO THOMAS WILLIAM"></interp>HORATIO THOMAS WILLIAM ELLIS</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a jeweller, and live in King-street, Covent-garden. On the 12th of September, about half-past nine o'clock, the prisoner came, and offered me some cuttings for sale—he said his master had sent him—I asked who his master was—he said, "Mr. Robertson"—I said I would send a shopman with him, and then he would not tell me where it was—I sent for an officer.</p>
